data.description: Move In Ready Pool home located in Port St. John. This 3 bed, 2 bath, home offers 1620 sqft of open living space. Tall vaulted ceilings, large eat in kitchen with newer stainless appliances. Roof only 2 years old, HVAC only 4 years old. Large screened in porch looking out to an amazing private back yard and large in ground pool. Perfect for entertaining or family fun. There are 2 large driveways with more than enough room for RV or boat parking. Great location with easy access to schools, shopping, and entertainment. Just a short drive to the space center, Orlando, and the beaches. This home is not to be missed. Call Today!
